{"tid":1208573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議：轉場遍地開花","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T09:48:38.000Z","uid":72590,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b644acfe0f5d616d63f5eb99ead99e47f1a1a75","tid":1208573,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"呢一刻立法會已經開返，留喺度嗰班打又唔夠打，除非真係已經夠物資夠人去玩火攻，唔係根本冇得玩落去<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議大家而家轉場做哂之前講話咩唔小心倒瀉花生油，向紅綠燈噴射現代藝術，然後過多幾個鐘等大家有共識之後就玩埋塞爆地鐵唔記得落車，等而家其他環頭掉咗去金鐘班狗冇得返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：gta私服香港mod"},{"pid":"f74df203ef66a8be5def9e3e12ff57222ae23dd5","tid":1208573,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab16d2d30923b4bcb42f2d390e33fbafd082c81","tid":1208573,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母得把口 你唔撚去做"},{"pid":"3e21a4db795accbfff5f6a5a44c0e07e11e1c5c8","tid":1208573,"uid":42860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"支持遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}